# Root .dockerignore — applies ONLY to builds whose context is the repo root (docker/seed.Dockerfile).
# The service/console images build from their own subdir contexts, so this does not affect them.
# Keep the seeder context to service/ + config/ + docker/ and drop everything heavy/irrelevant.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/out
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.github
console
react
sdk
docs
tests
*.md
